---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { Analytics } from '@vercel/analytics/react';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy | Invincible Title Card Generator" 
  description="Learn how Invincible Title Card Generator collects, uses, and protects your personal information. We are committed to protecting user privacy and data security."
  keywords="Invincible Title Card Generator, privacy policy, data protection, user privacy, security"
  type="article"
>
  <Analytics client:load />
  <Header />
  
  <main class="flex-grow py-10 px-4 mt-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-gray-800 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-yellow-400 mb-6 woodblock">Privacy Policy</h1>
      
      <div class="text-white space-y-6">
        <p class="text-gray-300">Last Updated: 2023-12-31</p>
        
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-yellow-300 mb-3">1. Information Collection</h2>
          <p>Invincible Title Card Generator ("we", "this website") respects your privacy rights. We collect limited information primarily to improve user experience and service quality.</p>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-yellow-200 mt-4 mb-2">Information we may collect includes:</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Usage analytics data such as page views, time spent, and feature usage</li>
            <li>Your device information including browser type, operating system, and screen resolution</li>
            <li>IP address and location information</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
        
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-yellow-300 mb-3">2. Information Usage</h2>
          <p>We use the collected information to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-2">
            <li>Provide, maintain, and improve our services</li>
            <li>Analyze user behavior to optimize website performance and user experience</li>
            <li>Detect and prevent security issues and abusive behavior</li>
            <li>Comply with legal requirements</li>
          </ul>
        </section>
        
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-yellow-300 mb-3">3. Data Sharing and Security</h2>
          <p>We do not sell, trade, or transfer your personal information to third parties. We may share limited information with:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-2 space-y-2">
            <li>Partners who provide analytics and service improvements (such as Google Analytics)</li>
            <li>Law enforcement or government agencies when legally required</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-2">We implement reasonable security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, use, modification, and disclosure.</p>
        </section>
        
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-yellow-300 mb-3">4. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>Our services are not directed to children under 13 years of age. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you discover we have inadvertently collected such information, please contact us and we will promptly delete it.</p>
        </section>
        
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-yellow-300 mb-3">5. Policy Changes</h2>
          <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Updated policies will be posted on the website with the last update date indicated. We recommend that you check this policy regularly to understand how we protect your information.</p>
        </section>
        
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-yellow-300 mb-3">6. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy, please contact us at:</p>
          <p class="mt-2"><a href="mailto:icnych@gmail.com" class="text-yellow-400 hover:underline">icnych@gmail.com</a></p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout> 